INFRO

Web pdf anotator. Creates images from pdf, and allow add comment to chosen places. Comments are displayed on left side (word like).

https://github.com/vitstradal/opraf

INSTALL

/*
 * opraf.db:
 *
$ sqlite3 db/opaf.db

CREATE TABLE opravy(
	id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
	pdf  TEXT,
	img_id TEXT,
	txt TEXT,
	status TEXT,
	au  TEXT,
	x INTEGER,
	y INTEGER
);

# set permissions,  webserver must have permission to write 
$ chomd o+w db/ db/opraf.db
$ chmod o+w tmp/

protect dir by  .htacces and .ht

